descriptionNullable:
### Context

I always enjoy Fairy Tale and I want to analyze the Grimm's Brother fairy tale dataset. 

### Content

The data were taken from the Grimm's Brother English Translation Fairy Tale https://www.grimmstories.com/en/grimm_fairy-tales/index

There are 4 columns in this data; Title, Story, Rating, Voter numbers.
 
### Acknowledgements

The data are taken from this website https://www.grimmstories.com/en/grimm_fairy-tales/index


### Inspiration

Many questions you could ask from this dataset, such as what topics often arise and why some fairy tale  are famous and some are not.
